                                課程簡介
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Introduction
                            





                                本課程設置，主要在藉由講授與討論過程中，增進研究生對公共行政與公共管理理論基本研究能力，以及提昇解決與改善公共部門實務問題之能力。

《 課程簡介 -- English 》
                                The objective of the class is to study the theories and practice of public administration. It is hoped that students can combine the theoretical learning with their working experience in the real world. The class offers theoretical research findings to students who may pursue further study. It also gives students related knowledge to improve their working ability and enhance their leadership potential. 











                                Material
                            

                                 
                            

                                上課教材
                            

                                 
                            





